===Etymology===
[[郵便]] ''postal service'' + 局 ''office''


===Noun===
[[Category:Japanese nouns|ゆうびんきょく]]
'''郵便局''' ([[ゆうびんきょく]], [[yūbinkyoku]])

# [[post office]]; [[postal centre]].
====Derived terms====
*[[特定郵便局]] (とくていゆうびんきょく, toutei yūbinkyoku) ''special post office''
*[[郵便局長]] (ゆうびんきょくちょう, yūbinkyokuchō) ''post master''
*[[郵便局員]] (ゆうびんきょくいん, yūbinkyokuin) ''postal clerk''


